Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black's jump at 1 is a sharp move.
\par After White 2, Black plays dansu at 3 and White is  captured.
\par
\par Even if White connects at A, it is useless.
\par
\par }
