Dia. 02 Dead?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It is an \cf1\b illusion\cf0\b0  if Black believes that he can capture White with the attachment at 1.
\par
\par However White's dansu at 2 is a \cf1\b big mistake\cf0\b0 . If Black goes out at 3, White is dead. White has shortage of liberties so he can't play at A.
\par
\par White is captured because 2 was a bad move.
\par
\par }
