Dia. 05 White's Good Move
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If Black follows the proverb which says "there is death in the hane", he starts with 1. However White 2 is the vital point for White as well.
\par
\par If White answers at A instead of 2, Black gets another chance. If Black plays at 2, White is dead.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
